{"tid":30186,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"77歲婆婆代祖父還書 單計罰款都要7.3萬","createTime":"2016-12-09T04:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T08:10:52.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3adfb2cf2ca8eb615fe731ec089f8ed844c63d1","tid":30186,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161208/large/1481188537_8bbd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161208%2Flarge%2F1481188537_8bbd.jpg&h=51a305fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國一間學校的圖書館，日前收到一位七旬婆婆歸還遲還的書籍－－足足遲了130年，單是罰款都要達7,500英鎊（約7.3萬港元），不過學校當然免除了有關罰款。<br />\n<br />\n還書的是77歲婆婆吉利特（Alice Gillett），她的祖父博伊科特（Arthur Boycott）在1886年借書後從未歸還，直至她近日收拾時，才發現這本遲還的圖書。<br />\n<br />\n古董書名為《The Microscope and its Revelations》，內有一個蓋印清楚看到書本是當年由薩默塞特赫爾福德教堂學校（Hereford Cathedral School）的圖書館借出，她於是將書寄回學校並附上道歉信。<br />\n<br />\n吉利特為祖父「偷書」致歉，「很抱歉告訴你，過往一名學生叫博伊科特，他看來偷了一本書，我不能想像學校沒有了它會怎樣。」<br />\n<br />\n吉利特指博伊科特成績優異，對鑽研蝸牛情有獨鍾，「祖母說他袋中永遠有蝸牛」，他其後成為博物學家（naturalist）和病理學家。校方發言人指：「很高興這本書獲歸還了，它的狀態仍然很好。」<br />\n<br />\n英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"9cbc07c7802afe27775fb6f693e5f15aefc3d95b","tid":30186,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:01:56.000Z","msg":"中學同學都借左學校書畢業都唔還<br />\n學校call佢都唔還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d66f504b3261f03730b877f966a3289e0b46f40","tid":30186,"uid":26130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:03:02.000Z","msg":"擺返百幾年你個孫就可以上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e359ba981bafffb0390b01383f8e735582e3ce","tid":30186,"uid":45138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"利申我畢業都冇還書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21e51f1d3780d219ed816a7c6724853fcb7aa95","tid":30186,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"諗起自己有本書未還 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39eaf77a6eded4aad01f3f8c8c44592b690bc55f","tid":30186,"uid":11059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:18:28.000Z","msg":"我都有本無還<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c6f6c11fb8f8f20561afdbd9cda82d46014d527","tid":30186,"uid":33979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擺返百幾年你個孫就可以上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時你間學校執左啦"},{"pid":"2cacbc3b5891508384f1aef7150b79da64799d00","tid":30186,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:46:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>擺返百幾年你個孫就可以上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時你間學校執左啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到时变左：特区第一实验中学（第15分校）"},{"pid":"6d43b47586359a5c9e1f15018fc1076598145eac","tid":30186,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:30:48.000Z","msg":"有同學借書唔還<br />\n結果要班會找數<br />\n幾年之後上佢屋企打牌<br />\n點撚知喺佢個書架見到本書"},{"pid":"4a2e6e89eca75df023b6f7ebfda30c2b05207cda","tid":30186,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:40:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc97731ba4e6f5f3756130f1b8b688cf2f500d61","tid":30186,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>擺返百幾年你個孫就可以上報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時你間學校執左啦</blockquote><br />\n當先你要有女朋友"},{"pid":"d49ca2fee8b2e90970d501eb1818b79ee2283ca2","tid":30186,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:43:17.000Z","msg